snippet.title: New Crony Corp Trailer before the holidays!
snippet.description:
If you're ready to climb to corporate greatness—or just hijack a truck for fun... Watch our new little trailer to see Crony Corp in action, now with 100% more humor and 404% less productivity. 

Don’t wait—hit that Steam wishlist now! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3195450/Crony_Corp/

(We kinda need you to so we know you wanna play. Just saying)
